    tmp = wp.cos((0.95 + (tmp + 0.58 * v2 + 0.75)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = 0.44
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.49 + v2 + 0.55)))
    v1 = wp.cos(0.21)
    v0 = v0
